"{\"uid\": \"breakingnews.ie-world-attacker-stabs-and-wounds-french-soldier-patrolling-paris-ahead-of-olympics-1650273.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Home  The Buzz  Sport  Quiz  Explained  Trending  Mobile menu  Theme  Home  The Buzz  Sport  Quiz  Explained  Trending  Search modal  Associated Press  A French soldier was stabbed outside a major train station in Paris on Monday, and the attacker was arrested, officials said.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 154, \"end\": 160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9985450706102196, \"rank\": 0.001339187939024765, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 214, \"end\": 219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999845386, \"rank\": 1.5425370489366882e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris is on high security alert, 11 days before the opening ceremony of the 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 279, \"to\": 369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 279, \"end\": 284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999845386, \"rank\": 1.5425370489366882e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A French military official said the soldier was taken to hospital with a shoulder blade injury but is not in a life-threatening condition.\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 373, \"end\": 379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9985450706102196, \"rank\": 0.001339187939024765, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An investigation was opened into attempted murder, and the suspect's identity was being confirmed, the prosecutor's office said.\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 639, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Authorities did not suspect terrorism as a motive at this stage, according to the national counterterrorism prosecutor's office.\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 769, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The soldier was among thousands of troops serving in the Sentinelle force for France's domestic security.\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 876, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 849, \"end\": 855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9945474963647949, \"rank\": 0.002641002184053336, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Interior minister Gerald Darmanin tweeted that the soldier had been patrolling at the Gare de l'Est train station in eastern Paris, and that the attacker was detained.\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 1045, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 878, \"end\": 895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Interior_minister\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.702877476145893e-21, \"text\": \"Interior minister\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Interior_minister\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Interior_minister\"}, {\"begin\": 896, \"end\": 902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\", \"score\": 0.9994985581463349, \"rank\": 0.00039737590067878415, \"text\": \"Gerald\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\"}, {\"begin\": 1003, \"end\": 1008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999845386, \"rank\": 1.5425370489366882e-11, \"text\"